{"tid":315830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★建造業人手荒 明年成立學院吸新血","createTime":"2017-07-10T10:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T04:44:51.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e119f2ae92b47f1a1001db40fa271b2ab5c61f72","tid":315830,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:00:02.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】建造業人手供不應求。發展局局長黃偉綸指建造業近年一直面對人力短缺和技術工人老化的問題，建造業議會推出各項培訓計劃，透過提供培訓及清晰的晉升階梯，吸引更多新血入行，傳承建築技術。建造業議會將於二○一八年上半年成立香港建造學院，提供更優質的技能培訓和提升工人的專業形象，吸納更多新人加入建造業。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170710/00176_028.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170710%2F00176_028.html&d=uigPdyvFM94kMxa8nD9tUdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=69a10f27\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170710/00176_028.html</a>"},{"pid":"3e4f0f2c6ffc72ebc05d66f91461ac7c0b1dd8d1","tid":315830,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:00:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56947791a656796e68cdc311d9d316cb9c913c8e","tid":315830,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:00:40.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"6d15b51dc8f9f6f16077e699cb9219a8824aa972","tid":315830,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:00:43.000Z","msg":"吸血<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea7e3e2d0844c34fac82b9fac8446d1c28a4dcb","tid":315830,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T10:00:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LM</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca